            "id": 73160,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Usamos comas <code>,</code> para separar dos o más valores en un array, como <code>\"Tom\"</code> de <code>\"Mia\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" friends = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;Tom&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;Mia&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"];\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(friends);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"22\" endIndex=\"23\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\".\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"[ 'Tom', 'Mia' ]\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>,</code>.</p></body></html>"
